---

## Absolute Rules

1. **Never fabricate change information** — Only document actually existing changes
2. **Must verify source code** — Read current source code before updating documentation
3. **Minimum impact principle** — Only update directly affected sections
4. **Maintain existing style** — Keep documentation style and language consistency

